		<title>18Sport and Recreation</title>
		<content>                                       
         {Caerphilly Recreation        
{Centre,}situated at Virginia Park is  
 the main sporting and recreational    
 facility in the town. Comprising of a 
 main hall, minor hall, swimming       
 pool,learner pool, weight training    
 room.four squash courts and an outdoor
 B.M.X. track.                         
                                       
           Sports catered for at the   
 centre are:                           
                                       
  Swimming     Roller Hockey           
  Gymnastics   Five a Side Soccer      
  Aerobics     Badminton   Keep Fit    
  Short Tennis Yoga        Table Tennis
  Circuit Training         Netball     
  Karate       Basket ball Volley ball 
  Weight Training          Squash      
                                       
                                       </content>
